orgien" lang="ka" hreflang="ka" class="interlanguage-link-target">ქართული</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ko"><a href="https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EC%A1%B4_%ED%9E%89%EC%8A%A4" title="존 힉스 — coréen" lang="ko" hreflang="ko" class="interlanguage-link-target">한국어</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-la"><a href="https://la.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ioannes_Ricardus_Hicks" title="Ioannes Ricardus Hicks — latin" lang="la" hreflang="la" class="interlanguage-link-target">Latina</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-mk"><a href="https://mk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%8F%D0%BE%D0%BD_%D0%A5%D0%B8%D0%BA%D1%81" title="Џон Хикс — macédonien" lang="mk" hreflang="mk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Македонски</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ms"><a href="https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Hicks" title="John Hicks — malais" lang="ms" hreflang="ms" class="interlanguage-link-target">Bahasa Melayu</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nl"><a href="https://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Hicks_(econoom)" title="John Hicks (econoom) — néerlandais" lang="nl" hreflang="nl" class="interlanguage-link-target">Nederlands</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nn"><a href="https://nn.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Hicks" title="John Hicks — norvégien nynorsk" lang="nn" hreflang="nn" class="interlanguage-link-target">Norsk nynorsk</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-no"><a href="https://no.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Hicks" title="John Hicks — norvégien bokmål" lang="nb" hreflang="nb" class="interlanguage-link-target">Norsk bokmål</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-oc"><a href="https://oc.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Richard_Hicks" title="John Richard Hicks — occitan" lang="oc" hreflang="oc" class="interlanguage-link-target">Occitan</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pl"><a href="https://pl.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Hicks" title="John Hicks — polonais" lang="pl" hreflang="pl" class="interlanguage-link-target">Polski</