		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="fr" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div id="" class="bandeau-container homonymie plainlinks hatnote" style=""><div class="bandeau-cell bandeau-icone" style="display:table-cell;padding-right:0.5em"><a href="/wiki/Aide:Homonymie" title="Aide:Homonymie"><img alt="Page d’aide sur l’homonymie" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Disambig_colour.svg/20px-Disambig_colour.svg.png" decoding="async" width="20" height="15" class="noviewer" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Disambig_colour.svg/30px-Disambig_colour.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Disambig_colour.svg/40px-Disambig_colour.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="272" data-file-height="200" /></a></div><div class="bandeau-cell" style="display:table-cell;padding-right:0.5em">Pour les articles homonymes, voir <a href="/wiki/John_Hicks_(homonymie)" class="mw-disambig" title="John Hicks (homonymie)">John Hicks (homonymie)</a> et <a href="/wiki/Hicks" class="mw-disambig" title="Hicks">Hicks</a>.
</div></div>
<div class="bandeau-container bandeau-article bandeau-niveau-ebauche plainlinks bandeau-container metadata ambox"><div class="bandeau-cell bandeau-icone" style="display:table-cell;padding-right:0.5em"><span style="white-space:nowrap;word-spacing:5px"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Circle-icons-profile.svg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Circle-icons-profile.svg/35px-Circle-icons-profile.svg.png" decoding="async" width="35" height="35" class="noviewer" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Circle-icons-profile.svg/53px-Circle-icons-profile.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Circle-icons-profile.svg/70px-Circle-icons-profile.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="512" data-file-height="512" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Fichier:Nuvola_United_Kingdom_flag.svg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d6/Nuvola_United_Kingdom_flag.svg/35px-Nuvola_United_Kingdom_flag.svg.png" decoding="async" width="35" height="35" class="noviewer" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d6/Nuvola_United_Kingdom_flag.svg/53px-Nuvola_United_Kingdom_flag.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d6/Nuvola_United_Kingdom_flag.svg/70px-Nuvola_United_Kingdom_flag.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="60" data-file-height="60" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Fichier:Emblem-money.svg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Emblem-money.svg/35px-Emblem-money.svg.png" decoding="async" width="35" height="35" class="noviewer" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Emblem-money.svg/53px-Emblem-money.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Emblem-money.svg/70px-Emblem-money.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="48" data-file-height="48" /></a></span></div><div class="bandeau-cell" style="display:table-cell;padding-right:0.5em"><strong class="bandeau-titre">Cet article est une <a href="